Calculating  Equilibrium  Constants 	  Experiments are very useful for determining equilibrium constants for various reactions. We are going to give a simple example of an experiment that could be done to determine the equilibrium constant for this reaction. The equilibrium constant expression for the reaction above has the following form: 
